Project Vision

Build an enterprise-grade platform that automatically identifies patients due for follow-ups, contacts them using multilingual AI voice agents, schedules appointments, synchronizes clinic calendars, updates clinic management systems, and provides actionable analytics while maintaining low latency and high reliability.

