Architecture Principles

- Event-driven microservices
- Streaming voice pipeline (<1 second conversational latency)
- Redis caching for availability and session state
- Function-calling for appointment booking
- PostgreSQL as source of truth
- Google Calendar and HMS synchronization
- Horizontal scalability and observability

